cd7c2373-7a05.name: Peugeot 208 GTi
cd7c2373-7a05.description: Back in the 1980s, the Peugeot 205 GTi took the hot hatch market by storm. It was fast, fun and cheap to buy, while offering all the practicality of the standard car. However, following the disappointing dynamic performance of subsequent Peugeot 206 GTi and 207 GTi models, enthusiasm for GTi-badged Peugeots inevitably waned. Fast forward to 2013 and the Peugeot 208 GTi was introduced, with bold claims that this was the car to recapture the magic of that 80s GTi experience. It was fast, fun and cheap to buy, while offering all the practicality of the standard car. However, following the disappointing dynamic performance of subsequent Peugeot 206 GTi and 207 GTi models, enthusiasm for GTi-badged Peugeots inevitably waned.
